<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhù fú nǐ yuè lái yuè cōng míng, zhù fú nǐ xué xí yuè lái yuè yòng gōng
 zhù fú nǐ shēn tǐ yuè lái yuè qiáng jiàn, yī shēng néng bèi zhǔ yòng.
 cóng xiǎo yào shú dú shèng jīng, fán shì dōu róng yào zhǔ míng.
 yé sū yǒng yuǎn jì zhe nǐ de míng zì, bì yǐn dǎo nǐ zǒu guò chūn xià qiū dōng.</lyrics>
<title>zhù fú zhǔ nèi xiǎo péng yǒu 迦南954</title>
